---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Agent Skills Discovery Guide | Is It Agent Ready?"
  description="Learn how to publish an Agent Skills discovery index at `/.well-known/agent-skills/index.json` so agents can discover and load your skills."
  canonical="https://isitagentready.com/checks/agent-skills"
>
  <section class="card" style="padding: 28px;">
    <h1 class="section-title">Agent skills discovery</h1>
    <p class="muted">
      Agent Skills discovery lets websites and platforms advertise reusable skills for coding agents and assistants. A published index points to the available skill artifacts and their digests.
    </p>
    <pre>{`{
  "$schema": "https://schemas.agentskills.io/discovery/0.2.0/schema.json",
  "skills": [
    {
      "name": "code-review",
      "type": "skill-md",
      "description": "Review code for bugs and regressions.",
      "url": "/.well-known/agent-skills/code-review/SKILL.md",
      "digest": "sha256:..."
    }
  ]
}`}</pre>
    <p class="muted">
      References:
      <a class="link" href="https://github.com/cloudflare/agent-skills-discovery-rfc" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"> Agent Skills Discovery RFC</a>
      {' · '}
      <a class="link" href="https://agentskills.io/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Agent Skills</a>
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
